modShortDescription: An older mod, which add some solid blocks that expand to cover the terrain, and then turn into water. Just to make filling up spaces with water easier.
modDescription:
This is an older mod, which add some solid blocks that expand to cover the terrain, and then turn into water. Just to make filling up spaces with water easier.

**[Download](https://github.com/dcsobral/7d2d/releases/download/2.0.0/LiquidWater-1.2.zip)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/17350-dcsobrals-mods/).
